  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (M&E)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Prepare and manage M&E cost estimates, BOQs, and tender submissions.</li><li>Monitor M&E project costs and provide financial insights.</li><li>Assist in evaluating M&E contractor claims and variations.</li><li>Coordinate with contractors and design teams on cost-related matters.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical/Electrical Engineering or Quantity Surveying.</li><li>At least 3 years’ experience in <strong>M&E works</strong> for <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Familiar with M&E systems and costing.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
